 respect shared between two players.<br><br>Thank you Jemmenai for helping demonstrate how to go about obtaining a first class rare item and to do it with RARE CLASS!  You are one of the few players that ever showed respect for my Trade.<br><br>I learned a lot from you.<br><br>Be Safe All,<br><br>Trafalgar,<br>26th Cleric of Tunare Drinal<br></p>&nbsp;<br>Trafalgar<br>neuroshock@bigfoot.com<br>(NeuroShock)</td></td></tr>
